<para id="fs-id1530124">A coil with circular cross section and 20 turns is rotating at a rate of 400 rpm between the poles of a magnet. If the magnetic field strength is 0.6 T and peak voltage is 0.2 V, what is the radius of the coil? If the emf of the coil is zero at <emphasis effect="italics">t</emphasis> = 0 s, when will it reach its peak emf?</para></problem>
