    <section id="fs-id1169737793828" class="section-summary"><title>Section Summary</title><list id="fs-id1169735522958">
    <item id="import-auto-id1169737786699">An electric generator rotates a coil in a magnetic field, inducing an emf<emphasis effect="italics"/>given as a function of time by
      <equation id="eip-841"><m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>emf</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mstyle fontstyle="italic"><m:mrow><m:mtext>NAB</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:mrow><m:mi>ω</m:mi><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext>sin</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mi fontstyle="italic">ωt</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>,</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{"emf"= ital "NAB"ω"sin"ωt} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math></equation>
where <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>A</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{A} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> is the area of an <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>N</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{N} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>-turn coil rotated at a constant angular velocity <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>ω</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ω} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> in a uniform magnetic field <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>B</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{B} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>.</item>
    <item id="import-auto-id1169737786855">The peak emf <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>emf</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{"emf" rSub { size 8{0} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> of a generator is
          <equation id="eip-714"><m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>emf</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mstyle fontstyle="italic"><m:mrow><m:mtext>NAB</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:mrow><m:mi>ω</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>.</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{"emf" rSub { size 8{0} } = ital "NAB"ω} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math></equation>
    </item>
    </list>
